                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "VhwUe",
                          "name": "Concise is a quiet, near-black workbench for the student who already knows what they want to learn. The interface stays out of the way so source material — equations, diagrams, a student's own writing — is what reads loudest. The brand mark concentrates that idea into a single typographic gesture.",
                          "fill": "#ffffffd9",
                          "content": "Concise is a quiet, near-black workbench for the student who already knows what they want to\nlearn. The interface stays out of the way so source material — equations, diagrams, a student's\nown writing — is what reads loudest. The brand mark concentrates that idea into a single\ntypographic gesture.",
